text:
...Since you said you wanted to think about the order,
I agreed to help, but... do you have any ideas, Mei?

Eh, but
aren't you going to do it alone──

I don't want to burden them any further
and I was the one who brought it up.

Besides, they have meetings tomorrow, right!?
So, it's just right for me to do it!

...If you're being considerate,
I wish you'd done it before getting them involved.
...Well, keep at it until you're satisfied.
